OVERVIEW

The EasyTool module aims to provide a easy to use function set

you can copy and paste some function to embed into your code as easy as possiable
youc can also make some modification on function

this package inlcude the time operate related function part of EasyTool

All of these feature is in a easy way.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following in the distribution
directory:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

or simply copy EasyTool.pm to your lib path

